א; Aleph; ox head. Strength / Leader.
ב; Bet; house. House / In.
ג; Gimel; walk. Walk / Carry.
ד; Dalet; door. Door / Pathway.
ה; He; behold. Behold / Reveal.
ו; Vav; nail. Add / Connect.
ז; Zayin; weapon. Cut / Nourish.
ח; Het; wall. Separate / Protect.
ט; Tet; basket. Surround / Contain.
י; Yod; hand. Work / Deed.
כ; Kaf; open palm. Open / Allow.
ל; Lamed; shepherd's staff. Teach / Toward.
מ; Mem; water. Chaos / Mighty.
נ; Nun; sprout. Continue / Heir.
ס; Samekh; prop. Support / Grasp.
ע; Ayin; eye. See / Know.
פ; Pe; mouth. Speak / Open.
צ; Tsadi; hook. Chase / Harvest.
ק; Qof; back of head. Condense / Behind.
ר; Resh; head. Head / First.
ש; Shin; teeth. Press / Consume.
ת; Tav; mark. Mark / Covenant.

Read right-to-left, beginning with Aleph.

